high_descs: Walk to the kitchen and go to the fridge.
take a plum out of the fridge.
walk past the hallway and go to the sink.
Throw the plum next to the sink.
go to the family room go to the shelf.
get the plum from the bookcase.
walk back through the hallway and go back to the room with the sink.
Throw the plum next to the sink with the other ball.
anns.task_desc: Get the Plum next to the Sink.

high_descs: Tour. Leave the room. Cross to the left. Continue. Then turn left. Reach the fridge. Turn left.
Open the refrigerator. Take the plum. Close the refrigerator.
Cross to the left. Exit and cross to the right. Continue to the sink on the left. Turn left.
Place the plum on the far left side.
Turn around. Turn right. Go straight ahead, enter the room. Turn left in front of the shelf.
Take the plum.
Turn left. Exit the sink. Turn left when you reach the sink on your left.
Place the plum before the other plum.
anns.task_desc: Look for two plum. Place them in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to exit the room and walk down the passage on the left and reach the fridge on the right.
Take out the plum from the fridge.
Turn left to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the bathroom sink.
Put the plum on the sink.
Head down the passage on the right to walk to the shelf.
Pick up the plum from the shelf.
Turn left to walk down the passage and reach the bathroom sink on the left.
Put the plum on the sink with the other plum.
anns.task_desc: Put two Plum balls on the Sink.
